      </symbol>
      <symbol type="2" id="123" code="510" name="Power line, cableway or skilift">
        <description>Power line, cableway or skilift.
The bars indicate the exact location of the pylons. If a section of a power line, cableway or skilift goes along a road or path (and does not offer significant additional navigational value) it should be omitted.

&lt;b&gt;Note: When drawing this symbol, press space to toggle placing the pylon symbols at new nodes.&lt;/b&gt;</description>
