      <symbol type="16" id="176" code="714" name=" Temporary construction or closed area">
        <description>Obvious temporary constructions like platforms for spectators and speaker, closed area for spectators, outside restaurant areas, etc. shall be represented in plan shape. A Temporary construction or closed area shall not be entered.
Minimum width: 0.5 mm.
Minimum area: 0.25 mm² (footprint 4 m²).</description>
